metadata.name: The Bearers of the Throne
metadata.description:
Issue #2 of Graveyard Stories

A martyr standing at the Pearly Gates, facing one of the Bearers of the Throne. The gates are defiled by the forces of corruption and the seraph is not a pure light anymore, but still caretaking God's throne.

The song is still there, trying to maintain order of all matter.

___
